#CAMERA 5
#phrase Hero  1
I heard that some of the pigs in the village have been killed lately?
#phrase Nsheriff  2
Yes, that's right, the wolves have never been so bold as to venture near our village at night.
#phrase Nsheriff  3
It seems as if there is a new pack of wolves living in the nearby forest.
#phrase Nsheriff  4
Word is that a white wolf was spotted there, I think he is the pack leader. If we kill him the wolf pack might disappear. Please take care of the problem!